WEBVTT

00:00:14.667 --> 00:00:18.742
Apa kesamaan film horor dan komedi?

00:00:18.742 --> 00:00:20.293
Dua genre ini mungkin sepertinya

00:00:20.293 --> 00:00:21.293
benar-benar berbeda,

00:00:21.293 --> 00:00:22.972
tapi keduanya sangat populer,

00:00:22.972 --> 00:00:23.985
mungkin karena

00:00:23.995 --> 00:00:25.365
kesamaan di antara keduanya:

00:00:25.365 --> 00:00:27.319
penggunaan ironi dramatik.

00:00:27.319 --> 00:00:28.733
Pertama, mari kita jabarkan.

00:00:28.733 --> 00:00:30.888
Ada 3 macam ironi.